Monitoring Scripts by Sebastian Muszytowski

Scripts are compatible to Nagios and Icinga

## Checks

	check_openvpn_running -> monitor whether openvpn (or any other pid) is running
	check_smsd -> this check can monitor smsd instances
	check_xfs_fragmentation -> check a xfs filesystem for fragmentation

## Misc

	icinga_mail.py -> alternative mail solution for icinga mailings
